Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass
.\env\Scripts\Activate.ps1
streamlit run main.py



✅ Here’s how to fix / stop it properly:

If you’re inside the Python shell (>>>) →
Type exit() or press Ctrl+Z then Enter (Windows).

If Streamlit is still running in the terminal (the one showing "Local URL: http://127.0.0.1:8501
") →
Stop it by pressing Ctrl+C once.